properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 14 at 2:21AM EST until February 14 at 9:00AM EST by NWS Tampa Bay Ruskin FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to one nautical mile or
less.

* WHERE...Tampa Bay waters, Coastal waters from Englewood to
Tarpon Springs FL out 20 NM and Waters from Englewood to
Tarpon Springs FL out 20 to 60 NM.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM EST this morning.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM EST THIS MORNING
